National Lake Morphometry (2013)

#Function to calculate shoreline development
#TO DO:
#  check for null lake
lakeShorelineDevelopment<-function(inLakeMorpho)
{
  return((gLength(inLakeMorpho$lake))/
                    (2*sqrt(pi*gArea(inLakeMorpho$lake))))
}
